content: Diplomatic mission of Singapore in the United KingdomDiplomatic mission The **High Commission of the Republic of Singapore** in [London](/wiki/London) is the [diplomatic mission](/wiki/Diplomatic_mission) of [Singapore](/wiki/Singapore) in the [United Kingdom](/wiki/United_Kingdom). Also accredited as the Embassy of Singapore to Ireland and Iceland. The building forms one of a group of [Grade II](/wiki/Listed_building) listed stucco buildings along the western side of [Wilton Crescent](/wiki/Wilton_Crescent), in the [Belgravia](/wiki/Belgravia) district. ## Gallery - Official site This article about a London building or structure is a stub.
